Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE FINAL AVAN STYLE TECHNIQUE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! I'm not...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A Morph spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too bad that\Nthat wasn't the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eventually show you dimwits\Nthat I'm on a different level up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneaky little imp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystvearn's gone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's Hadlar?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remember killing him...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Valge tower. We're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry\Nor Leona won't make it! Let's charge in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:02:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Blizzblaze Legion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let you get to Master Flazzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bagi!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to hang around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-Popp!\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merazoma!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Frostburn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Now for the Dancing Flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes! {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyadaruko!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything's possible\Nif we work together, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Flazzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sitting back and waiting\Nwith the hostage just isn't my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That axe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your savagery ends here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were helping them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I told you.\NYou can't kill a guy like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Does that mean he beat Hadlar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered I owed you\Nmuch like I did Hadlar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So I came back from the depths of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no escape now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?! You giving up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My Blizzblaze Curse Field's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And with two Legion Commanders\Non your side, even I can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's time to face the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's acting awfully well-behaved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flazzard's not one\Nto say something like that.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll admit defeat and release\Nthe Princess of Papnica?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I lose everything,\NI'll never give up a chance at victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what was that about facing the fact?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant the fact that\NI won't get through this unscathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The final attack I'm about to use\Nhurts me real bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer not to use it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark King Vearn, grant me glory and victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're throwing away your medal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so important about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The day Sovereign Rock Castle\Nwas completed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was the first time we\NSix Legion Commanders had gathered.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh great Dark King Vearn,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the Six Legion Commanders to lead\Nthe Dark Army are before you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This Sovereign Rock Castle shall be our\Nbase as we plunge the world into darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and offer it to you, King Vearn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Hadlar. I am most pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My king.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To celebrate the Six Legion Commanders,\NI shall grant a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the Infernal Emblem. Consider it\Nthe greatest symbol of loyalty to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, whoever believes\Nthemself worthy may take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What intense flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But we must prove our loyalty\Nto King Vearn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Flazzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when he gained the title\N"Blitz Captain of the Dark Army."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That medal is a symbol of his glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,To him, it's almost worth life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And he threw it away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who needs past glory?!\NIf it will let me claim new victory...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...to risk my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He self-destructed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-destructed? With this weak a blast?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in death he seeks glory. How pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... a fragment of Flazzard's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It really can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one of these rocks is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,These are bullets of rock!\NThey're Rock Bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how strong you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you break,\Nthe more of me there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my final attack method,\N{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Rock Bullet Shrapnel Detonation!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll just freeze them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyadaruko!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops. He has ice rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're up, big Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,MAGIC BULLET GUN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.58,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}FIVE FINGER FLARES{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, aim for his core!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,His core?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. He said all of these rocks\Nare him, but that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's an energy rock life-form created by\NHadlar using Forbidden Magic.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There should only be one core rock\Nthat's the source of his life.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have to find it and break it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,His core...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But how can I find a single rock\Namong all of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you do, Flazzard can't be beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing can defeat my ultimate attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good! I can't find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No human can shatter my core hidden here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't beat him!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:12:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can I cut an enemy I can't see?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you can cut the unseen,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,your blade will become\Nthree, or even five times more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An enemy I can't see!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why he had me train!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The air... in other words,\Nyou slice the emptiness.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hoimi! spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like hiding behind Crocodine\Nspared you some damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Flazzard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His flames and cold are dwindling!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I look pathetic to you, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This final attack method\Ndrains my life drastically.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you risk death just to win?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My being has no history.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been barely a year\Nsince Master Hadlar created me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want achievements!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Achievements no one can beat whether\Nthey live to be a hundred or a thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you prove yourself\Nthrough something other than fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who asked for your pity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The thrill of victory!\NThe jealous glares of my peers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They are what fulfill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you all would just die,\Nthen everything will be perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see that you can't win?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to use my final attack now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:14:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the greatest technique of\Nmy master, Avan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never successfully done it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If I fail, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,if I can do it... I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just bluffing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That attack...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Blizzblaze Shrapnel Detonation!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't dodge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Avan Style Sword Technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Air Slash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If that pathetic attack is his greatest\Ntechnique, I guess Avan's not much, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No... I failed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it really beyond me, Master?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That last one, the Air Slash,\NI don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on.\NMaster's explained it a ton of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then did you understand it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Mage, so I don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That sort of thinking is why\Nyour progress is so slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do\Nagainst an evil swordsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, an evil swordsman\Nwouldn't use this skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Air Slash requires an Aura of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,An Aura of Justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are monsters in this world\Ncreated by dark magic.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Air Slash is an attack\Nthat vanquishes such evil beings.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To do it, first...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you charge your blade\Nwith the Aura of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to release it towards\Nthe enemy's true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The difficult part is determining\Nwhere the enemy's true form is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike the weak spots of normal monsters,\Nyou can't see it with your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:17:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\NI'm sure you'll pick it up eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How to see an unseen enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good, Master!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't... see it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll burn you to a crisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,His Air Slash wasn't a complete failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You're telling me\Nthat attack grazed my core?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll do it until I succeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! If you use\Nthat attack again, it'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll all die first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the risk of getting burned\Nis what makes gambling fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's blinded by the glory of victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes, Dai!\NIt's a showdown between our final attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Rock Bullet Shrapnel Detonation!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Air Slash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like with this many targets,\Nthere's no hope for any accidental hits!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I win this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it no good?!\NIsn't there anything Dai can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's forgetting that Air Slash\Nis an attack that slices the empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike the earth and the sea, you can't\Nsee the empty no matter how hard you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,remind him of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Look with your inner eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My inner eye?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As an attack, your Air Slash\Nis already complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not yet a mastered technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you see your enemy\Nwith your inner eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it will be a true technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll become a true Air Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him with... my inner eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Air Slash strikes dark energy\Nwith light energy to destroy evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I could never master it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:20:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time for you to inherit\Nthe greatest Avan Style technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As if such a fantasy attack\Ncould defeat my ultimate attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't find it\Nbecause I keep looking for it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sense it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The life energy of everyone here!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel a warm presence.\NThat must be Maam.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's Hyunckel.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The big one is Crocodine.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's Popp over there.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something's coming!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A giant evil energy!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's approaching me,\Ngiving off malice everywhere!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:20:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}his core!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flazzard!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Air Slash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like another dud...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my... My core!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,my target!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:32.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:44.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:57.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:01.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:08.19,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:14.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:19.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.22,0:23:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai's Air Slash struck Flazzard.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just when victory is at hand, Mystvearn,\Nthe Shadow Vizier appears before Dai.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After turning into Dark Aura,\Na spiteful Flazzard attacks Dai again.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai and Flazzard's final showdown begins.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.32,0:23:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.74,0:23:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Now I Slice Everything"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.74,0:24:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.70,0:24:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,
